<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Thank you for contacting Kingsbridge.</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">In respect of your request to exercise your rights according to the GDPR, <b>we are unable to delete your details from our systems</b>. However, <b>we have suppressed you from receiving marketing communications</b>.</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>We are unable to delete your details at this time as these are required to enable us to act as an insurance broker/agent in the placement of your insurance policy. </b>We have regulatory and contractual requirements to hold data in relation to insurance policies we have placed.</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>This confirms that policies are and were in fact in place and enables us to respond to any current and future claims you may submit or may be submitted against you by a third party.</b> Employers’ Liability and Public Liability claims can be submitted many years after an event and consequently this data will be held on file for a period of one hundred years following expiry of policies in accordance with our data retention policy.</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Please note that <b>you may hear from us again in the next 30 days whilst we update your details</b>.</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Our data fair processing notice can be accessed via the following link: https://www.kingsbridge.co.uk/fair-processing-notice/</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Your rights under GDPR can be accessed via the following link: https://ico.org.uk/</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Kind regards,</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!User.FirstName}</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Customer Service Team</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">T: 01242 808 740</font></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>